text: appeal from primary judge where discretionary relief sought
power and function of appellate court

high court rules, o. 20, r. 29; o. 26, r. 18; o. 63, r. 2. brambles holdings ltd. ("brambles") was defendant in an action brought by the trade practices commission. brambles applied to franki j. in chambers to have certain paragraphs of the statement of claim struck out. franki j. refused the order sought. brambles appealed.
